I have a like new, barely used Advantage Arms .22 conversion kit that will fit various Glock frames up to Gen 3 (will NOT work on Gen 4). It is specific about ammo type and the instructions with the kit spells that ammo out, but if you stick in those guidelines this is the best kit out there for .22 conversions. LOCAL FACE-TO-FACE cash transactions only! I will not ship nor ask that you send me money.

NOT RECOMMENDED: CCI Mini Mag Hollow Points, any Winchester ammo, Federal Ammo, Remington Thunderbolts, CCI Stinger, hyper velocity ammo

Note: Remington Golden Bullets work quite well, however you will get more light stikes and inconsistent loads than with the other recommended ammo.
